        "subject": "LU-19361 tests: fix replay-single/61c with active hosts",
        "message": "LU-19361 tests: fix replay-single/61c with active hosts\n\nWhile running replay-single/61c in hard failure failover mode,\nthe active OST host was changed after the OSS failed over to\nits partner. So, the test needs to call $(osts_nodes) again\nto get the active hosts afer running \"fail ost1\".\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=replay-single\nTest-Parameters: trivial env=FAILURE_MODE=HARD \\\n  clientcount=4 mdtcount=1 mdscount=2 osscount=2 \\\n  austeroptions=-R failover=true iscsi=1 \\\n  testlist=replay-single\n\nChange-Id: Ibac8d70719080023a6a4a0a0b0614864a779d7b0\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/61408\nReviewed-by: Emoly Liu <emoly@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Frederick Dilger <fdilger@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
